  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Community!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/aa9ae770c241fb9427fa6f332e7db1bb.avif?t=1764164546\" width=612 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/031dc221f640f04621cc5b3d0ae56420.poster.avif?t=1764164546\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/031dc221f640f04621cc5b3d0ae56420.webm?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/031dc221f640f04621cc5b3d0ae56420.mp4?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be a <strong>BOXI</strong> and tear your opponents' bodies apart while preventing them from shredding your muscular character in this physics-based multiplayer brawl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the stage traps to become the champion of the ring.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep a cool head to knock out your opponents in the most violent and fun way!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/d3dd9de1f27e6537fa9a329e97d97dce.avif?t=1764164546\" width=415 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split-screen multiplayer</strong> and online mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remote Play Together support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with controller or keyboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your <strong>Boxi</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several game modes such as 2 vs 2 or <strong>up to 8 players</strong> all against all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat system based on <strong>physics</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of scenarios to fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multitude of <strong>traps</strong>and <strong>weapons</strong> in each scenario.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievement system.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/703b3a4315df095ac0a9ffe3643f103e.poster.avif?t=1764164546\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/703b3a4315df095ac0a9ffe3643f103e.webm?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/703b3a4315df095ac0a9ffe3643f103e.mp4?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Among the game modes that will be available in <strong>Knock'Em Out</strong> we highlight:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathmatch</strong>: Knock out all the players until you are the last one standing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bomb Tag</strong>: Escape from the player with the bomb, the last one standing will win  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/list].</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Title Champion</strong>: Take the title and defend it in order to become the champion<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/05b319ddba346959843d657fef14d8a3.poster.avif?t=1764164546\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/05b319ddba346959843d657fef14d8a3.webm?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/05b319ddba346959843d657fef14d8a3.mp4?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/aa9ae770c241fb9427fa6f332e7db1bb.avif?t=1764164546\" width=612 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/031dc221f640f04621cc5b3d0ae56420.poster.avif?t=1764164546\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/031dc221f640f04621cc5b3d0ae56420.webm?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/031dc221f640f04621cc5b3d0ae56420.mp4?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be a <strong>BOXI</strong> and tear your opponents' bodies apart while preventing them from shredding your muscular character in this physics-based multiplayer brawl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the stage traps to become the champion of the ring.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep a cool head to knock out your opponents in the most violent and fun way!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/d3dd9de1f27e6537fa9a329e97d97dce.avif?t=1764164546\" width=415 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split-screen multiplayer</strong> and online mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remote Play Together support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with controller or keyboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your <strong>Boxi</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several game modes such as 2 vs 2 or <strong>up to 8 players</strong> all against all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat system based on <strong>physics</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of scenarios to fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multitude of <strong>traps</strong>and <strong>weapons</strong> in each scenario.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievement system.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/703b3a4315df095ac0a9ffe3643f103e.poster.avif?t=1764164546\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/703b3a4315df095ac0a9ffe3643f103e.webm?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/703b3a4315df095ac0a9ffe3643f103e.mp4?t=1764164546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Among the game modes that will be available in <strong>Knock'Em Out</strong> we highlight:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathmatch</strong>: Knock out all the players until you are the last one standing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bomb Tag</strong>: Escape from the player with the bomb, the last one standing will win  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/list].</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Title Champion</strong>: Take the title and defend it in order to become the champion<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192900/extras/05b319ddba346959843d65